#: ../../library/venv.rst:154
msgid ""
"``clear`` -- a Boolean value which, if true, will delete the contents of any "
"existing target directory, before creating the environment."
msgstr ""
"``clear`` -- 真偽値で、真の場合環境を作成する前に既存の対象ディレクトリの中身"
